When a document is set to this element, modifying the document without invoking <links><link cref="::vl::presentation::elements::GuiDocumentElement::NotifyParagraphUpdated(vint,vint,vint,bool)@s:vl.presentation.elements.GuiDocumentElement" /></links> will lead to undefined behavior.</summary> <param name="value">The document.</param> </Document>
